They sit back in their comfy computer chair, sitting in front of their x-Ghz computer, sipping some ice-tea, watching the sanitized war coverage and turning up the AC a bit, cause they feel a sweat bead coming on. While the majority of people in the world huddle around a water hole which produces brownish water for them to drink.<br>
<br>
I'm very sorry if those pictures of a <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>WAR</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> disturb you, but maybe they should. If everyone's disturbed by those pics, maybe we (as a human race) won't produce any more reasons for pictures like this. &quot;You may say I'm a dreamer...&quot;<br>
