<br>
War is an awful thing, but because of human nature it's a necessary thing.  I don't see anything wrong with someone giving us the opportunity (No you don't have to look if you don't want to so don't use that excuse) to get a better idea of what war really is.   <p>Ragnon Xython v1.0<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><br>
